"}, {"start": 700.0200000000001, "end": 700.84, "text": " We're always safe."}, {"start": 700.84, "end": 702.4000000000001, "text": " This gives us more s**t to talk for when we go to LSU,"}, {"start": 702.4000000000001, "end": 703.24, "text": " at least."}, {"start": 703.24, "end": 704.0600000000001, "text": " Thank you, guys."}, {"start": 704.0600000000001, "end": 704.9000000000001, "text": " Thank you."}, {"start": 704.9000000000001, "end": 705.74, "text": " Thanks for having us."}, {"start": 705.74, "end": 707.1600000000001, "text": " Take the log."}, {"start": 707.1600000000001, "end": 708.0000000000001, "text": " Let's go."}, {"start": 709.2, "end": 710.0400000000001, "text": " Not you."}, {"start": 710.12, "end": 711.28, "text": " I still suck."}, {"start": 713.28, "end": 714.4, "text": " Notre Dame."}, {"start": 714.4, "end": 715.24, "text": " What's up, man?"}, {"start": 715.24, "end": 716.0799999999999, "text": " Oh my God."}, {"start": 716.0799999999999, "end": 716.9, "text": " Nice to meet you, bro."}, {"start": 716.9, "end": 717.74, "text": " Dude, I'm a huge fan."}, {"start": 717.74, "end": 718.5799999999999, "text": " I appreciate it, bro."}, {"start": 718.5799999999999, "end": 719.42, "text": " Thank you, bro."}, {"start": 719.42, "end": 720.26, "text": " Let's do it, bro."}, {"start": 720.26, "end": 721.0799999999999, "text": " Thanks, man."}, {"start": 721.0799999999999, "end": 721.92, "text": " Go to LSU, or?"}, {"start": 721.92, "end": 722.76, "text": " Unfortunately, after that one."}, {"start": 722.76, "end": 723.5799999999999, "text": " Good game, man."}, {"start": 723.5799999999999, "end": 724.42, "text": " I appreciate you, bro."}, {"start": 724.42, "end": 725.56, "text": " I thought we were gonna lose anyway, so."}, {"start": 725.56, "end": 727.5999999999999, "text": " Yeah, I thought you were too, and then like you guys won"}, {"start": 727.5999999999999, "end": 729.24, "text": " and now I'm just like depressed, so."}, {"start": 729.24, "end": 730.0799999999999, "text": " It's okay, man."}, {"start": 730.0799999999999, "end": 730.92, "text": " Yeah."}, {"start": 730.92, "end": 732.8, "text": " How do you think A&M fans felt"}, {"start": 732.8, "end": 734.68, "text": " the past f**king eight seasons, man?"}, {"start": 734.68, "end": 736.8399999999999, "text": " I know, you guys fell off after Johnny Manziel."}, {"start": 736.8399999999999, "end": 738.88, "text": " And y'all got a natty about what, four years ago?"}, {"start": 739.04, "end": 740.4399999999999, "text": " Shout out, Joe Burrow."}, {"start": 740.4399999999999, "end": 741.28, "text": " That's a lot."}, {"start": 741.28, "end": 742.1, "text": " Appreciate it, man."}, {"start": 742.1, "end": 742.9399999999999, "text": " Thanks for hosting us."}, {"start": 742.9399999999999, "end": 744.12, "text": " I thought he recognized me,"}, {"start": 744.12, "end": 746.28, "text": " but nah, he was just a genuinely nice dude."}, {"start": 746.28, "end": 747.4, "text": " Shout out, bro."}, {"start": 747.4, "end": 748.24, "text": " Shout out, bro."}, {"start": 749.6, "end": 750.4399999999999, "text": " What?"}, {"start": 750.4399999999999, "end": 752.4399999999999, "text": " Let's go."}, {"start": 752.4399999999999, "end": 753.28, "text": " What do you mean?"}, {"start": 753.28, "end": 754.12, "text": " Let's go."}, {"start": 754.12, "end": 754.9399999999999, "text": " You know what it means?"}, {"start": 754.9399999999999, "end": 755.78, "text": " Let's go."}, {"start": 755.78, "end": 756.62, "text": " Let's go."}, {"start": 756.62, "end": 757.4399999999999, "text": " Let's go."}, {"start": 757.4399999999999, "end": 758.28, "text": " I'm out."}, {"start": 758.28, "end": 759.24, "text": " Damn, we really are taller in person."}, {"start": 759.24, "end": 761.74, "text": " That's like the best compliment ever."}, {"start": 761.74, "end": 762.58, "text": " Let's do it, man."}, {"start": 762.58, "end": 763.42, "text": " Huge, big fan."}, {"start": 763.42, "end": 764.24, "text": " Nice to meet you."}, {"start": 764.24, "end": 765.08, "text": " Nice to meet you."}, {"start": 765.08, "end": 766.44, "text": " Dude, I've been waiting for you to be here."}, {"start": 766.44, "end": 767.32, "text": " Thank you so much."}, {"start": 767.32, "end": 768.72, "text": " Your fan base is too nice."}, {"start": 769.5600000000001, "end": 770.4, "text": " Hey, that was a great game."}, {"start": 770.4, "end": 771.22, "text": " That was solid."}, {"start": 771.22, "end": 772.88, "text": " It was a great game until the fourth quarter."}, {"start": 772.88, "end": 775.0400000000001, "text": " I was preparing myself for the opposite."}, {"start": 775.0400000000001, "end": 775.88, "text": " At least you're honest."}, {"start": 775.88, "end": 777.32, "text": " Why the are they so nice here?"}, {"start": 777.32, "end": 778.1600000000001, "text": " Like why?"}, {"start": 778.1600000000001, "end": 778.98, "text": " Are you okay?"}, {"start": 778.98, "end": 779.82, "text": " Why are you getting close to me?"}, {"start": 779.82, "end": 780.64, "text": " Next one you should get."}, {"start": 780.64, "end": 781.9200000000001, "text": " I didn't want to get head butted again."}, {"start": 781.9200000000001, "end": 782.76, "text": " I'm sorry."}, {"start": 782.76, "end": 783.58, "text": " You have a great night."}, {"start": 783.58, "end": 784.4200000000001, "text": " You too, thank you."}, {"start": 784.4200000000001, "end": 785.26, "text": " Fuck LSU."}, {"start": 785.26, "end": 786.48, "text": " Fuck LSU, bro."}, {"start": 786.48, "end": 788.96, "text": " Well chat, it's officially time to go back home."}, {"start": 788.96, "end": 790.8000000000001, "text": " I appreciate you all for tuning in."}, {"start": 790.8000000000001, "end": 793.24, "text": " This week's video was more passive than not."}, {"start": 793.24, "end": 795.02, "text": " Although I did get hit the hardest"}, {"start": 795.02, "end": 796.24, "text": " I've ever been hit in my life."}, {"start": 796.24, "end": 797.08, "text": " It is what it is."}, {"start": 797.08, "end": 798.36, "text": " We're out here getting content for you guys."}, {"start": 799.0, "end": 799.84, "text": " And also, I did not start that."}, {"start": 799.84, "end": 800.96, "text": " I just was checking on a girl."}, {"start": 800.96, "end": 802.2, "text": " Simply seeing if she was okay."}, {"start": 802.2, "end": 803.14, "text": " And bro tweaked out."}, {"start": 803.14, "end": 804.6, "text": " So, you know, it is what it is."}, {"start": 804.6, "end": 806.96, "text": " We got Isaac out of jail before he even went to jail."}, {"start": 806.96, "end": 807.8000000000001, "text": " Which is clutch."}, {"start": 807.8000000000001, "end": 808.8000000000001, "text": " No one needs to go down."}, {"start": 808.8000000000001, "end": 809.8000000000001, "text": " Comment for you, Isaac."}, {"start": 809.8000000000001, "end": 811.48, "text": " Like the video to keep supporting us."}, {"start": 811.48, "end": 813.44, "text": " As always, again, I appreciate you all."}, {"start": 813.44, "end": 815.22, "text": " I appreciate Isaac and Scotty for coming along."}, {"start": 815.22, "end": 816.6, "text": " Most importantly, I thank God."}, {"start": 816.6, "end": 817.44, "text": " And I'll see you all next week."}, {"start": 817.6400000000001, "end": 820.5200000000001, "text": " It's night, it's night."}, {"start": 820.5200000000001, "end": 823.2, "text": " We're going up, up, up, up, up."}]}